b9 <code>#a-\u9898\u540d</code>\uff09\u3002</p>"},{"location":"contests/2026-the-2019-polish-collegiate-programming-contest-amppz-2019/#_4","title":"\u590d\u76d8","text":"<p>\u5f85\u8865\u3002</p>"},{"location":"contests/2026-the-2019-polish-collegiate-programming-contest-amppz-2019/#_5","title":"\u76f8\u5173\u94fe\u63a5","text":"<ul> <li>\u5f85\u8865</li> </ul>"}]}